Regression Analysis of valence unsgined on SEND and SST Dataset together. We are comparing attentions across these two datasets not dictionary.

# this version, i do not include any hand picking labels. in way, we can have a baseline
Test <- read_csv("~/Dropbox/EMNLP2020-Attention-TW/code/warriner_valence/Test_send2sst_fine.csv")

nlap <- Test[(Test$count_sst>min_val&Test$count_send>min_val),]

ggplot(nlap, aes(x=send, y=sst)) + 
  geom_point(shape=18, alpha = 3/10)+
  stat_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, size = 1, linetype="dashed", color="darkred", fill="blue") +
  labs(title="SST Attention & SEND Attention", x="SEND Attention", y = "SST Attention")
